				</div>
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>How long do non-surgical facial treatments last?</h3>
					<p>The duration varies by treatment: Botox lasts 3-4 months, dermal fillers last 6-24 months, chemical peels results can last several months, and laser treatments may require maintenance sessions. Regular treatments are needed to maintain results, but many patients find the convenience and minimal downtime worthwhile.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Are surgical facial rejuvenation procedures safe?</h3>
					<p>When performed by a board-certified plastic surgeon like Dr. Johar, surgical facial rejuvenation procedures are generally safe. All surgeries carry some risk, but complications are rare with proper technique and patient care. A thorough consultation helps minimize risks and ensures you are a suitable candidate for surgery.</p>
